definitions.definition: Half past ; a half-hour (30 minutes) after the last hour.
examples: The time is 9:30; it is half nine.

definitions.definition: A half-hour to ( preceding ) the next hour.
examples: In some countries, " half seven" means 6:30.

main_definition: ( UK , Ireland ) Half past ; a half-hour (30 minutes) after the last hour.
secondary_definitions: ( Discuss this sense) ( rare , see usage notes ) A half-hour to ( preceding ) the next hour.
